sentences.en: And sibling ( a good friend ) went to sing KTV.
sentences.cn: 和兄弟姐妹 ( 好朋友 ) 一起去KTV唱歌.

sentences.en: Bob: She was there, and she looked as young as my sibling.
sentences.cn: 鲍勃: 她也在, 她看起来像我的姊妹一样年轻.

sentences.en: But when we fight it's kinda like sibling rivalry.
sentences.cn: 不过这种争吵其实好像同胞间的竞争.

sentences.en: Detected two sibling members with the same name: % 1.
sentences.cn: 检测到同名的两个兄弟成员: %1.

sentences.en: Do your parents, grandparents or sibling ever had any of the following?
sentences.cn: 你的父母, 祖父母,外祖父母,兄弟姐妹是否有下列病?

sentences.en: Gordon: Sis, why don't we have a sibling rivalry?
sentences.cn: 戈登: 妹妹, 为什么我们之间不来个同胞争斗?

sentences.en: It only returns the very next sibling, not all next siblings.
sentences.cn: 这个函数只返回后面那个紧邻的同辈元素, 而不是后面所有的同辈元素.

sentences.en: Many of us hate living in the shadows of a more successful sibling.
sentences.cn: 我们很多人都讨厌活在更为成功的手足的阴影下.

sentences.en: Molly: They have a real sibling rivalry going on.
sentences.cn: 莫莉: 他们之间是真正的同胞争斗.

sentences.en: Most young smokers are influenced by their friends’ and older siblings’ smoking habits.
sentences.cn: 大多数年轻的吸烟者都是因为他们的朋友或者哥哥姐姐有吸烟习惯而受影响的。

sentences.en: Sibling relationships also influence children's peer status and peer relationships.
sentences.cn: 兄弟姐妹关系也影响儿童的同伴交往技能和同伴地位.

sentences.en: Sibling rivalry often causes parents anxieties.
sentences.cn: 手足之争常让父母忧心忡忡。

sentences.en: Starting offset of the field relative to the previous sibling or delimiter.
sentences.cn: 与以前的同辈或分隔符相关的字段的起始偏移量.

sentences.en: The word'sib " is a contraction of'sibling ".
sentences.cn: “同胞 ” 是“同胞兄弟 ” 的简称.

sentences.en: There's a friendly sibling rivalry between my sister and me.
sentences.cn: 我和姐姐之间有一种良性的手足之间的竞争.

sentences.en: These latter, therefore, represent'sibling species'such as have been described in other organisms.
sentences.cn: 因此后者呈现出诸如在其它生物 中曾 描述过的那种姊妹种.

trans.tran_cn: 兄弟，姐妹，[生]同科，同属，[人]氏族成员
